---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <main class="p-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-4">Collaborators</h1>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            The AURA protocol is an open and collaborative initiative. Its early development was supported by students, researchers, and educators committed to AI transparency.
        </p>

        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700">
            <li>Fausto David Cortés Rojas – Lead Researcher & Protocol Architect</li>
            <li>Biomedical Engineering students from UVM – Dataset curation and testing</li>
            <li>Contributors from CINVESTAV Bioelectronics Section</li>
            <li>OpenAI tools used with attribution and consent</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">
            This site is hosted at <strong>aura.org</strong> and serves as a living reference for the development and adoption of the AURA standard.
        </p>
    </main>
</Layout>
